description.en-CA: Featuring a straight-leg fit with a slightly flared hem, the Nike Legend 2.0 Slim Poly Women's Training Pants improve upon the original version with design updates that flatter and enhance comfort, whatever your workout. The subtle v-shaped seam that connects the waistband to the legs enhances your body's curves, while the other flattering seams sculpt the lines of the legs and let you move without distractions. The new triangle-shaped gusset helps reduce ride-up, and power mesh at the interior waistband helps eliminate creases and lines for a smooth look.
description.en-US: Featuring a straight-leg fit with a slightly flared hem, the Nike Legend 2.0 Slim Poly Women's Training Pants improve upon the original version with design updates that flatter and enhance comfort, whatever your workout. The subtle v-shaped seam that connects the waistband to the legs enhances your body's curves, while the other flattering seams sculpt the lines of the legs and let you move without distractions. The new triangle-shaped gusset helps reduce ride-up, and power mesh at the interior waistband helps eliminate creases and lines for a smooth look.
description.fr-CA: Offrant une jambe droite et un ourlet légèrement évasé, le pantalon d'entraînement moulant Legend 2.0 en polyester pour femmes de Nike est une version améliorée du modèle original dont les mises à jour s'avèrent flatteuses et confortables, peu importe le type d'entraînement. La couture légèrement incurvée qui relie la taille aux jambes accentue les courbes du corps, tandis que les autres coutures sculptent le contour des jambes; le tout permet un entraînement exempt de distraction. Le nouveau gousset triangulaire prévient toute remontée disgracieuse, tandis que le filet robuste à l'intérieur de la taille élimine les plis et assure un aspect lisse et épuré.

description.en-CA: The Nike Dri-FIT Regular Fit Legend 2.0 Women's Training Pants offer freedom of movement, lasting comfort and a smooth look for any workout regimen. Dri-FIT recycled polyester fabric to wick sweat away and help keep you dry and comfortable. A straight leg for a slimming fit through the hip and thigh. Low-rise for a modern look. Fitted through the hip and thigh, flared hem. Strategically placed seams to visually shape and lift. Waistband with an upward tilt at back for coverage. Powermesh material inside waistband to smooth and flatten waist. Low-profile, internal pocket to hold small items like keys and a cell phone. At least 10 recycled plastic bottles were used to make these pants.
description.en-US: The Nike Dri-FIT Regular Fit Legend 2.0 Women's Training Pants offer freedom of movement, lasting comfort and a smooth look for any workout regimen. Dri-FIT recycled polyester fabric to wick sweat away and help keep you dry and comfortable. A straight leg for a slimming fit through the hip and thigh. Low-rise for a modern look. Fitted through the hip and thigh, flared hem. Strategically placed seams to visually shape and lift. Waistband with an upward tilt at back for coverage. Powermesh material inside waistband to smooth and flatten waist. Low-profile, internal pocket to hold small items like keys and a cell phone. description.fr-CA: Le pantalon d'entraînement Legend 2.0 en coton Dri-FIT de coupe régulière pour femmes de Nike procure une grande liberté de mouvement, un confort durable et une allure épurée, peu importe le type d'entraînement. Le tissu de polyester recyclé est doté de la technologie Dri-FIT qui évacue la sueur et vous permet de demeurer au sec en tout confort. La jambe droite procure une coupe amincissante le long des hanches et des cuisses. La taille basse en modernise l'allure. Ajusté le long des hanches et des cuisses, doté d'un ourlet évasé. Coutures réparties stratégiquement pour créer une forme et un soulèvement visuellement plaisant. La bande à la taille est inclinée vers le haut à l'arrière afin de fournir une couverture accrue. Le tissu en filet robuste à l'intérieur de la ceinture affine et flatte la taille. Des poches internes discrètes permettent de ranger de menus objets tels que des clés ou un cellulaire. Au moins dix bouteilles de plastique recyclées ont tété utilisées pour confectionner ce pantalon.

description.en-CA: Featuring a fit that hugs your body from hip to knee, the Nike Legend 2.0 Tight Poly Women'S Training Capris improve upon the original version with design updates that flatter and enhance comfort, whatever your workout. The slightly reduced waistband width and increased rise help keep you covered when bending and stretching. The waistband also tilts up in the back for a natural fit and a streamlined appearance while helping to prevent roll-down. The subtle v-shaped seam that connects the waistband to the legs enhances your body's curves, while the other flattering seams sculpt the lines of the legs and let you move without distractions. The new triangle-shaped gusset helps reduce ride-up, and power mesh at the interior waistband helps eliminate creases and lines for a smooth look.
